{"word":"διφροφορέω","slug":"διφροφορέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διφροφορέω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to carry in a chair</i> or <i>litter</i>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to travel in one</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to carry a campstool</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:διφροφόρος'><el>διφροφόρος</el></a>\n"}]}